---

Relationship examples

This is where the app shines:

“LineFlow depends_on Timer Engine”

“QueueGauge expands Job Leasing”

“Atlas Gallery example_of Asset Pipeline”



---

Performance considerations

Prefetch related links

Limit backlink display to 25

Paginate search results



---

Smoke tests

1. Create entry “Timer Engine”


2. Create entry “LineFlow Board”


3. Link LineFlow → Timer Engine (depends_on)


4. Entry page shows related links


5. Backlink shows on Timer Engine page


6. Search returns entries




